metadata.description: Mini Mich is an ecosystem of NFTs, land, coins, carbon certificates, and games. A collection of 10K fully-3D hipster fashion apes designed by award-winning artist, inspired by our own zeal for fashion, sneakers, gadgets, and environmentalism. Mini Mich NFT brings fun to holders with customizable accessories. You can mint your own unique NFTs tailored to your own fashion taste through burning accessory NFTs. The possibility is limitless. Mini Miches live in a metaverse called Mini Mich Land, a digital land for the most trendy brands and vocal environmentalists. You, the coolest you, come to the Land and make your voice heard in Mini Mich world!
